'''黑素皮质素受体'''（{{lang-en|Melanocortin receptor}}，缩写'''MCR'''）是七[[跨膜结构域|跨膜]]的[[G蛋白偶联受体|G蛋白偶联受体]]中[[视紫质|视紫质]]家族的一员，在人类基因组包括五个成员<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://arbl.cvmbs.colostate.edu/hbooks/pathphys/endocrine/bodyweight/melanocortins.html |title=Melanocortins and the Melanocortin Receptor<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2007-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070411014246/http://arbl.cvmbs.colostate.edu/hbooks/pathphys/endocrine/bodyweight/melanocortins.html |archive-date=2007-04-11 |url-status=dead }}</ref>，各自对不同[[黑素皮质素|黑素皮质素]]有不同亲和活性<ref name="pmid14535656">{{cite journal |vauthors=Voisey J, Carroll L, van Daal A |title=Melanocortins and their receptors and antagonists |journal=Current Drug Targets |volume=4 |issue=7 |pages=586–97 |date=October 2003 |pmid=14535656 |doi= 10.2174/1389450033490858}}</ref><ref name="pmid16412534">{{cite journal |vauthors=Hadley ME, Dorr RT |title=Melanocortin peptide therapeutics: historical milestones, clinical studies and commercialization |journal=Peptides |volume=27 |issue=4 |pages=921–30 |date=April 2006 |pmid=16412534 |doi=10.1016/j.peptides.2005.01.029 }}</ref><ref name="pmid19456331">{{cite journal |author=Dores RM |title=Adrenocorticotropic hormone, melanocyte-stimulating hormone, and the melanocortin receptors: revisiting the work of Robert Schwyzer: a thirty-year retrospective |journal=Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences |volume=1163 |issue= 1|pages=93–100 |date=April 2009 |pmid=19456331 |doi=10.1111/j.1749-6632.2009.04434.x }}</ref>：

* {{Gene|MC1R}}，[[MC1R|MC1R]]与遗传色素沉着有关。
* {{Gene|MC2R}}，[[MC2R|MC2R]]也被称为[[ACTH受体|ACTH受体]]，能特异性结合[[促腎上腺皮質激素|促腎上腺皮質激素]]（ACTH）。
* {{Gene|MC3R}}，[[MC3R|MC3R]]
* {{Gene|MC4R}}，[[MC4R|MC4R]]缺陷是常染色体[[显性|显性]][[肥胖症|肥胖症]]的一个原因，占所有早发性肥胖病例的6%<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Farooqi IS, Keogh JM, Yeo GS, Lank EJ, Cheetham T, O'Rahilly S |title=Clinical spectrum of obesity and mutations in the melanocortin 4 receptor gene |journal=N. Engl. J. Med. |volume=348 |issue=12 |pages=1085–95 |year=2003 |pmid=12646665 |doi=10.1056/NEJMoa022050}}</ref>。
* {{Gene|MC5R}}，[[MC5R|MC5R]]。

